<p><strong>Combustion Monitoring<br></strong>Also included in the Industrial Series is the 7330 Combustion Sensor for Caterpillar G3600 series engines. This sensor immediately alerts the engine management at the first sign of abnormal combustion. The same robust construction and innovative design found in the 7306 spark plug can be found in the Bosch Industrial Series Combustion Sensor.</p>
<p> </p>
